(230, 1, '2023-05-16 18:32:02', '2023-05-16 21:32:02', '<!-- wp:uagb/container {\"block_id\":\"ddecf583\",\"variationSelected\":true,\"isBlockRootParent\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-ddecf583 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\"><!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"e92b3c07\",\"classMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-e92b3c07\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>Researches associated with VODAN BR</strong></h2></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To implement the VODAN BR platform, different research fronts were proposed. These researches account for the participation of graduation, masters e doctorate students from UFRJ and UNIRIO, and, when needed, healthcare specialists from partnered hospitals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/container {\"block_id\":\"2a085330\",\"variationSelected\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-2a085330\"><!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"4ea1f2b1\",\"classMigrate\":true,\"headingTag\":\"h3\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-4ea1f2b1\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>Dissertation Research</strong></h3></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th>Project</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Plano de Gestão de Dados Ativos</td><td>Active Data Management Plan Elaboration for the VODAN BR Project.</td></tr><tr><td>Coleta de Metadados em processos ETL para gerar Proveniência FAIR</td><td>Collection of provenance metadata from the process of transforming data into RDF format (ETL4LOD).</td></tr><tr><td>Metadados de proveniência para reuso de dados em Covid-19</td><td>Investigation on the percepetion of healthcare researchers on provenance metadata needed for reuse of data on COVID-19 research.</td></tr><tr><td>Modelo semântico para coleta de dados em Covid-19</td><td>Semantic model study for data collection on COVID: a vocabulary review.</td></tr><tr><td>Compartilhamento de dados de pesquisa no contexto da COVID-19</td><td>Analysis on the requirements of research funders in COVID-19 and researchers\' practices and perceptions of sharing research data on COVID-19.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table --></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/container {\"block_id\":\"9fb2a1d0\",\"variationSelected\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-9fb2a1d0\"><!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"e6bf451d\",\"classMigrate\":true,\"headingTag\":\"h3\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-e6bf451d\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>Researches on Final Papers</strong></h3></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th>Projeto</th><th>Descrição</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>ETL de Dados Clínicos (HUGG)</td><td>Extraction, transformation and cleaning of structured and non-structured clinical data for loading into a relational database.</td></tr><tr><td>ETL4FAIR</td><td>ETL4LOD integration to GraphDB and to FAIR DP. API implementation allowing for the pubishing of RDF data and their provenance on tripestore GraphDB; their respective metadata, dataset and FAIR DP distribution.</td></tr><tr><td>Bussiness Inteligence</td><td>Panel elaboration for analysis of collected data from COVID-19 patients’ care.</td></tr><tr><td>Ambiente de Contingência para Dados de Pesquisa</td><td>Elaboration of a project that promoites high availability for the infraestructure on the VODAN-BR Project.</td></tr><tr><td>Módulo de Gestão de Pesquisas</td><td>Implementation of the application eCRF VODAN module, designed to create and update forms for research. The published forms can be used in the Forms Management module to collect data that will later be transformed into linked data, associated with semantic artifacts from the research domain.</td></tr><tr><td>ML em dados não estruturados de Prontuários</td><td>Implementation of a solution for the extraction of relevant information from unstructured data in medical records.</td></tr><tr><td>ML em dados não estruturados de Prontuários</td><td>Analysis of the terms adopted in non structured fields in medical records and their correlation with COVID-19.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table --></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/container {\"block_id\":\"a3c3ce86\",\"variationSelected\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-a3c3ce86\"><!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"52cab0e6\",\"classMigrate\":true,\"headingTag\":\"h3\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-52cab0e6\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>Research and Group Works in Support Areas of the Platform</strong></h3></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th>Projeto</th><th>Descrição</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Processo de FAIRificação - Workflow</td><td>Elaboration of FAIRification workflow to meet the specifics of the VODAN-BR project.</td></tr><tr><td>Piloto VODAN BR</td><td>Implementation of Pilot Project for proof of concept of the VODAN BR platform.</td></tr><tr><td>Estudo sobre a disponibilização de dados anonimizados de pacientes do HUGG para a pesquisa</td><td>Study on the structure to be adopted to make anonymized COVID-19 patient data available.</td></tr><tr><td>Evolução do Módulo de Gestão de Formulários e aprimoramento do módulo de Gestão de Usuários</td><td>Evolution of the module of forms management, making it compatible with the changes resulting from the research management module.</td></tr><tr><td>Estrutura de Metadados do FAIR DP</td><td>Elaboration of a proposal of a metadata scheme structure, employing DCAT, to organize the FAIR DP of VODAN BR.</td></tr><tr><td>Ferramental de apoio a Gestão de Metadados</td><td>Study of available tools for the metadata management and metadata schemes to be adopted into the Project. In 2021, analysis were made with the CEDAR Workbench tool, and its ways of interacting with other platform sotwares, such as ETL4LOD.</td></tr><tr><td>Vocabulários e Ontologias</td><td>Study of vocabularies and ontologies to complement info on WHO’s forms treated with the “Others” option.</td></tr><tr><td>Metadados de Proveniência</td><td>Research Problem: Which metadata (patterns) would be used to register the provenance of the process of “FAIRification” of data on COVID-19 obtained from partnered hospitals of thje Project until they’re depoisted in a repository?</td></tr><tr><td>Análise de dados estruturados e não estruturados de Prontuários Informatizados para Pesquisa Clínica</td><td>Study of the WHO Form for COVID associated with the analysis of unstructured information recorded in the Anamnesis (patient reception) and in the evolutions (hospitalization follow-up). In 2021, the meetings held with the HUGG\'s health team allowed the establishment of preliminary assumptions for the extraction of information from structured and unstructured data. These premises are being used by the Final Papers’ team regarding the ETL of electronic medical records data transformation and will evolve according to the project\'s needs.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table --></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/container {\"block_id\":\"15c9289b\",\"variationSelected\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-15c9289b\"><!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"a2dbd020\",\"classMigrate\":true,\"headingTag\":\"h3\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-a2dbd020\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>Graduation Courses Projects</strong></h3></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Banco de Dados I Course</strong><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Course-concluding paper. For the development of the works, proposals were established for evolutions in the scheme of the support database, elaboration of SQL queries and development of WEB applications, implementing relevant functionalities for the project, such as: management of access control to the Support for Clinical Research database, registration of patient information in a survey module in the Support for Clinical Research database, and queries and visualizations about the data stored in the Support for Clinical Research database.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Laboratório de Sistema da Informação II Course</strong><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Prepare a Dataverse environment based on established metadata on FAIR DP specifications, in order to optimize the process of publishing the data and metadata of the VODAN BR project;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Implement a solution that acess both FAIR DP and the Dataverse, via API. The tool must perform searches using the metadata available in FAIR DP, and search, when requested, the datasets in the repository in a more user-friendly way. Despite presenting an interface for humans, FAIR DP publishes codified information that can hinder user access. By working with standardized terms, an application would be able to search terms in other semantic artifacts, including in other languages, aiding the search process.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/container --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/container -->', 'Projects', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '209-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-05-16 18:32:02', '2023-05-16 21:32:02', '', 209, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=230', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
